sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { Container, Role, User, Avatar } from './styles' interface UserProps { nickname: string isBot?: boolean } const UserRow: React.FC = ({ nickname, isBot }) => { return ( {nickname} {isBot && BOT} ) } const UserList: React.FC = () => { return ( Online - 1 Bots - 5 Offline - 18 ) } export default UserList
